    "MissionGiver": "Covalex Independent Contractors",
    "Title": "Small Covalex Shipment Needs Recovering",
    "TitleKey": "Covalex_RecoverCargo_Easy_Title",
    "Description": "Hiya,\n\nI've got a client who's been messaging me all morning about a shipment they were supposed to receive and when I checked up on the cargo it turns out that it's sitting completely still in the middle of space.\n\nThis is obviously bad for a number of reasons, and not just because I had to spend 20 minutes getting yelled at. Can you head over to <EM4>~mission(Location|Address)</EM4> and see what happened? The original contract called for a ship that could carry <EM4>~mission(MissionMaxSCUSize) cargo containers</EM4> so make sure you've got that and a <EM4>heavy-duty tractor beam</EM4>.\n\nOnce you've got the cargo, can you make sure it's delivered to the freight elevator at <EM4>~mission(Destination|Address)</EM4>? Thanks a bunch.\n\n~mission(Contractor|SignOff)\n\nElla Tieno \nJr. Logistics Coordinator \nCovalex Shipping   \n'Anything you need, anywhere you need it.' \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nCovalex Shipping is a limited liability corporation. To encourage timely deliveries and prevent fraud on cargo hauls, Covalex Shipping will set a delivery time limit and upon expiration, any undelivered cargo will be considered stolen and treated as such. Total payment will be prorated according to the percentage of cargo successfully delivered.",
    "DescriptionKey": "Covalex_RecoverCargo_Easy_Description",
    "DisplayDescription": "Hiya,\n\nI've got a client who's been messaging me all morning about a shipment they were supposed to receive and when I checked up on the cargo it turns out that it's sitting completely still in the middle of space.\n\nThis is obviously bad for a number of reasons, and not just because I had to spend 20 minutes getting yelled at. Can you head over to <EM4>[Location|Address]</EM4> and see what happened? The original contract called for a ship that could carry <EM4>32 SCU cargo containers</EM4> so make sure you've got that and a <EM4>heavy-duty tractor beam</EM4>.\n\nOnce you've got the cargo, can you make sure it's delivered to the freight elevator at <EM4>[Destination|Address]</EM4>? Thanks a bunch.\n\n[Contractor|SignOff]\n\nElla Tieno \nJr. Logistics Coordinator \nCovalex Shipping   \n'Anything you need, anywhere you need it.' \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nCovalex Shipping is a limited liability corporation. To encourage timely deliveries and prevent fraud on cargo hauls, Covalex Shipping will set a delivery time limit and upon expiration, any undelivered cargo will be considered stolen and treated as such. Total payment will be prorated according to the percentage of cargo successfully delivered.",
